Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:05.99,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,MUSIM KEDUA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.70,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,BALADA PILU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.99,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,AWAL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:12.42,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,GENTING & SOLUSI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.48,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,UNTUK EN, CHIDARUMA\NHARI HOKI DI BULAN MARET
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:54.01,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,AKHIR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kita bisa mulai membagikan\Nmakanan untuk para pendatang baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu produksi\Ndan menjual Bubuk Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harta di wastu ini lebih dari cukup\Nuntuk kita semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos masih belum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Ton dan Natsuki sudah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya mereka ingin mengumpulkan\Nsemua orang dan menunjukkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!\NTak ada satu luka pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jenis sihir pertahanan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami gagal menangkap Kikurage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sihir Natsuki bangkit\Nsaat bertarung dengan keluarga En!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti pelindung\Nyang bisa mementalkan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, lain kali ayo coba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau Natsuki bisa\Nmenggunakan sihir sehebat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia tak perlu ada di Mata Silang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa kaya dengan sihir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu, mata kirimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kami kembali ke wastu\Ndan menyembuhkan lenganku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku juga punya tato silang di mata ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski sudah bisa menggunakan sihir,\Naku akan selalu jadi Mata Silang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cuma keinginan pribadiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku boleh tinggal di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dapat masalah, kamu akan\Nmelindungi kami dengan sihir itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Semuanya—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, kamu resmi menjadi\Nanggota Mata Silang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menyangka akan berubah\Njadi pria dan kembali ke sini lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu jadi sangat tampan, Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan kamu,\Njadi sosok yang sangat berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, pakaian ini sangat berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian itu berat karena latihan sihirmu\Nmasih berlangsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, sihir yang mengubah gendermu\Nhanya bertahan empat jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, kamu akan kembali ke\Nwujud aslimu, jadi harus hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti.\NEmpat jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekitar pukul sembilan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah dengar ini dari sesama iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di wastu ini, kabarnya ada kamar\Nyang hanya menyimpan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}barang berharga\Nyang iblis hadiahkan pada En.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu ingat sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, waktu itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}En pernah membawaku ke ruangan aneh\Ndan terus mengoceh soal kehebatannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu ruangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seingatku, ada semacam objek yang berfungsi\Nsebagai pintu tersembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita cari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruangan ini juga dipakai\Npengurus keluarga En?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ini kamar Noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ambil barang-barang berharganya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uang saja sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita cari petunjuk keberadaan\Nanggota keluarga En
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang mungkin masih bersembunyi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat Bos kembali, kita foto bersama juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tak sabar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, lama tak jumpa,\Npara pengurus Mata Silang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ri-Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat tanda silang yang ingin kuhapus ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa masuk dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang ingin kutanyakan pada kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Risu, seperti yang kami bilang,\Nkami tak tahu siapa yang membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, Dokuga mungkin\Nmenyembunyikan sesuatu dari kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia tahu banyak tentangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bukan masalah.\NAku akan tanya langsung padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tak akan membiarkanmu\Nmenemui Dokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, coba hentikan aku,\Ndasar para sampah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakannya.\NAku bisa merasakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Niat membunuh kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga,\Ntak ada penjaga di pintu masuk ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah aku kerja paruh waktu\Ndi tempatnya Tanba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, aku harus mencari Risu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokuga, apa yang akan kamu lakukan\Npada Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa saja mati terbunuh seperti Risu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki bisa terbunuh?\NMereka sedang bahas apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Bos mengincar sihir Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak akan diam saja, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menentangnya!\NKita harus cari cara—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memberi Natsuki misi\Nuntuk menjauhkannya dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, aku akan bicara dengan Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memohon padanya\Nuntuk tak membunuh rekan kita lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi, aku ingin\Nmencoba percaya pada Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Bos yang memberi kita\Nalasan untuk hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi kita, sampah yang tak bisa sihir,\Ndia memberi jalan selain mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kamu benar, Dokuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo percaya pada Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia akan paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Area ini ruang pribadinya En.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak hal seperti\Nkamar tidur untukku dan Kikurage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ada di dekat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini area khusus pengurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku mulai ingat sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunjukkan tangan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus periksa asap kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya beberapa pembuat onar\Nmenemukan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mungkin pengurus Mata Silang.\NBagaimana ini, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, cepat tunjukkan tangan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga bagian dari latihanmu.\NCoba lawan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan cari bukunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian ini berat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Dokuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetsujo, kamu lengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Mata Silang saling bertarung?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau terus memakai ini,\Naku akan terbunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan...\N- Sombong dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa terus meladeni kalian.\NSaatnya kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari tadi kamu lihat apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rekam medis Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat ini, sudah jelas\Nkalau Caiman manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi saat periksa rekamnya,\Nada hal yang membuatku penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caiman itu korban sihir,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukannya wajar kalau ada yang janggal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menjelaskannya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi ingin bahas ini dengan Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini alasan\Nkepala Caiman beregenerasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sudah sebulan sejak itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi penasaran apa yang terjadi\Npada Caiman dan Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia harusnya kabur lewat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!\NKita kehilangan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wastu besar memang merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, Dokuga,\Nkepalamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti lewat lorong.\NAyo kejar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah, sepertinya kita berhasil\Nmenjauh dari mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ini kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku harus sembunyi\Ndengan Mata Silang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga pasti akan\Ndapat masalah kalau diam saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, aku ingat sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Patung batu ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}En teliti membuat ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ini patung iblis,\Ntak ada yang berani menyentuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak salah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yakin,\Nmelakukan itu pada patung iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu! Ini pintu masuk\Nke ruang harta karun En!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga ikut masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sembunyi sampai situasinya tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kenapa aku harus ikut?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku sibuk—\N- Sudah, ayo masuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ruangan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gudang harta karun\Nyang sangat dijaga En.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harta karun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini malah seperti tumpukan sampah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kamu siapa?\NDari tadi kamu sok akrab—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu belum sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyamar jadi pria dengan sihir\Nuntuk menyelinap ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dilihat, benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan bohong, Sialan!\N- Aduh, sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir, lukanya tak parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, saatnya cari bukunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, aku bawa roti kari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski mengaku Nikaido,\Nkita baru bertemu beberapa hari lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tak ingat wajahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu, ini bukunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu datang jauh-jauh ke sini\Ncuma untuk mencuri buku itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku ini berisi informasi yang kubutuhkan\Nuntuk menggunakan sihirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, gawat!\NSudah pukul sembilan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, sekarang kamu percaya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang,\Naku bukan pria bernama Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ngeyel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, aku yang menamaimu Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, saat kepalamu kembali normal,\Nkamu melupakanku, Hole, dan gioza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gioza...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!\NAku tak tahu apa pun soal gioza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar para pengurus melawan monster!\NAyo kita lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada ribut apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian, mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini berbahaya!\NMundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan.\NIni memalukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak bisa menyerang Kutukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus cari cara untuk mengusirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat dia bicara dengan Dokuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melawannya dengan sihirku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, mundur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Natsuki, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk hitam yang di sana itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan gegabah, Natsuki.\NSialan terkutuk itu tak kenal lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ternyata dia bisa menggunakan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau situasinya gawat,\Nkita bantu Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakannya.\NAku bisa merasakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Niat membunuhmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Risu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kamu di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil kutangkap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus apakan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gantung dia di luar jendela!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NAda ribut apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Risu berubah jadi Kutukan\Ndan menyerang kami lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, Natsuki mengalahkannya dengan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata sihir Natsuki bisa melawan Kutukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki, ikut kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Risu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oi, Risu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Risu, bangun!\N- Jadi monster yang tadi itu Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikaido, bukunya sudah dapat.\NSebaiknya kita segera pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kawajiri.\NLama tak jumpa, Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aikawa, kamu ikut dengan kami juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa ikut dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gantinya, tolong jaga dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia partnerku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Risu partnermu?\NJadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, serahkan padaku.\NTapi, apa yang akan kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, kamu menghindariku dari awal.\NKenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal ingatanmu\Nsudah kembali seperti semula.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NKamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dekati aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dekati aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu punya kehidupanmu sendiri,\Njadi apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo makan gioza lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memberimu diskon 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikaido, ayo cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah muak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah muak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah muak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu menolak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu, sejak awal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak pernah ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!\NDapat misi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokuga memberiku misi khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini pencarian penyihir elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya, aku mau Bos melihat sihirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, dia bilang jangan mencolok\Ndan pergi lewat pintu belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku akan keluar menjalankan misi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sudah beres, aku boleh foto\Nbersama semua anggota Mata Silang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menginginkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bo-Bos...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kita tahu sejauh ini di Episode 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.10,0:24:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada petunjuk di berkas medis Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.27,0:25:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aikawa menitipkan Risu pada Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.19,0:25:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki ingin berfoto bersama semua orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.94,0:25:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu yang akan kita ketahui di Episode 24,\Nmasih tersembunyi dalam kekacauan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.99,0:25:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah Dorohedoro!
